OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FMostly dry and bright start
OL,6,Fbut turning cloudier for a time as
OL,7,Fscattered showers move south, with a
OL,8,Fcooler northerly breeze developing.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FBright
OL,11,For sunny spells and a chance of
OL,12,Fshowers each day, these more likely on
OL,13,FFriday. Cooler into midweek, with
OL,14,Fpatchy overnight rural frost possible,
OL,15,Fmilder later. Winds generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
